Priority: optional
Build-Depends: debhelper (>= 10), perl (>= 5.6.0-16)
Maintainer: NOKUBI Takatsugu <knok@daionet.gr.jp>
Standards-Version: 4.3.0
Homepage: https://osdn.net/projects/nkf/
Vcs-Git: https://salsa.debian.org/debian/nkf.git
